<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Appointment - TechTrainers</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #292524;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fafaf9;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706 0%, #b45309 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        
        .appointment-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .appointment-detail {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .appointment-detail:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #64748b;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .client-info {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .client-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: #d97706;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #6b7280;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #292524;
            color: #a8a29e;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #d97706;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #166534;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üéØ New Appointment Booked!</h1>
            <p>You have a new client session scheduled</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong>{{trainerName}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>Great news! A new appointment has been booked with you. Here are the details:</p>
            
            <div class="appointment-card">
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üìÖ Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">‚è∞ Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üí™ Session Type:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value highlight">{{sessionType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">‚è±Ô∏è Duration:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{duration}} minutes</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üìç Location:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{location}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="client-info">
                <h3>üë§ Client Information</h3>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Name:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{clientName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Email:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{clientEmail}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Phone:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{clientPhone}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Fitness Level:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{clientFitnessLevel}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if clientNotes}}
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Notes:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{clientNotes}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="{{acceptUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">‚úÖ Accept Appointment</a>
                <a href="{{rescheduleUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">üìÖ Reschedule</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p><strong>üìù Next Steps:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Review the client's fitness level and notes</li>
                <li>Prepare your session plan accordingly</li>
                <li>Contact the client if you need to discuss anything</li>
                <li>Confirm the appointment by clicking the button above</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> Please confirm or reschedule this appointment within 24 hours to maintain our service quality.</p>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p>Need help or have questions? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> or visit our <a href="{{supportUrl}}">Support Center</a>.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>The TechTrainers Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                <strong>TechTrainers</strong> - Empowering Fitness Through Technology<br>
                <a href="{{companyWebsite}}">{{companyWebsite}}</a> | 
                <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a><br>
                <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a> | 
                <a href="{{privacyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>